                                   PART III
 
ITEM 10. DIRECTORS AND EXECUTIVE OFFICERS OF THE REGISTRANT.
 
  THCR is the general partner of THCR Holdings. The partnership agreement
governing THCR Holdings provides that all business activities of THCR must be
conducted through THCR Holdings or subsidiary partnerships or corporations. As
the sole general partner of THCR Holdings, THCR generally has exclusive
rights, responsibilities and discretion in the management and control of THCR
Holdings. THCR Funding is a wholly owned subsidiary of THCR Holdings.
 
DIRECTORS AND EXECUTIVE OFFICERS
 
  The following table sets forth certain information concerning each of THCR's
directors and executive officers:
 
