1995. Mr. Ribis has been the Chief Executive Officer of Plaza Associates since
February 1991, was President from April 1994 to February 1995, and was a
member of the Executive Committee of Plaza Associates from April 1991 to May
29, 1992, and was a director and Vice President of Trump Plaza GP from May
1992
 
